self.in_fqfn = _generate_foobarbatz_file(100, dir_name=self.tmp_dir,
    quoting='quote_nonnumeric')
schema = _generate_foobarbatz_schema()
self.schema_fqfn = _write_schema_file('foobarbatz', schema, dir_name=self.
    tmp_dir)
self.cmd = (
    """%(pgm)s %(in_fqfn)s
                         -d ','
                         --validschema %(schema)s
                         --quoting quote_nonnumeric
                         --outgood %(outgood)s
                         --outerr  %(outerr)s
                         -s
                   """
     % {'pgm': self.pgm, 'outgood': self.outgood_fqfn, 'outerr': self.
    outerr_fqfn, 'in_fqfn': self.in_fqfn, 'schema': self.schema_fqfn})
runner = envoy.run(self.cmd)
status_code, stdout, stderr, good_recs, err_recs = self.get_outputs(runner)
os.system('cat %s' % self.in_fqfn)
assert status_code == 0
